Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果姊姊知道我寫了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了預防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是先寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊就跟媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有姊姊在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我真的很感謝姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這種話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本完全無法表達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我發生了什麼不測
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不要難過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我會去動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓自己更幸福給妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會變成能夠守護重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠守護姊姊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（巧海 舞衣）\N所以，請妳要等我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的姊姊


